## Subagent Protocol

For parallel tasks, spawn:
```javascript
sessions_spawn({
  task: "[ACTION] — report back with [FORMAT]",
  label: "brief-descriptive-name",
  runTimeoutSeconds: 300,
  thinking: "off"
})
```

Don't poll. Let them report back.

